node.text:
Being stuck at home under quarantine doesn’t mean you can’t train your body like you once did in the gym. That’s why I love @fightcamp , it’s fully equipped with everything you need for a total body workout, and when I need a change of scenery, I move it from indoors to my outdoor porch. 
There’s a lot going on right now, taking time for yourself and staying in shape is more important than ever. As an entrepreneur and a busy Mom with home schooling responsibilities, I can’t always get a full workout in...thats what makes Fight Camp perfect! You can schedule the number rounds you have time for! Best of all, Fight Camp has empowered me by keeping both my body and mind ready for whatever challenges are yet to come. #fightcamp #telliapproved 🎥: @alex.toderica

node.text: Had so much fun modeling for Glaudi and showcasing our collection this season with @dustofgods @artheartsfashion ! Thank you Erik, Johnathan Sutton, Johanna , Deontay, Antonio, Pate, Lauren, Alex, Sarah, Sacha, TT, Dai-B, my dad, and all my friends and family who came to support such an amazing event !! Love you all !! Until next time!! With love , Telli

node.text: So excited to announce my new fragrance @dtellifragrances. Travel sizes are now available for purchase and regular sizes will be available mid August.
